<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Dependencies</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Install<sp/>apt<sp/>packages<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>versioning<sp/>provided<sp/>in<sp/>`system_requirements.MD`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Install<sp/>Mosquitto</highlight></codeline>
