<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>MQTT<sp/>Server</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Run<sp/>`mosquitto<sp/>-v`<sp/>in<sp/>terminal</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
