<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Running</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Run<sp/>`mosquitto<sp/>-v`<sp/>in<sp/>terminal.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">After<sp/>building<sp/>with<sp/>build.sh,<sp/>run<sp/>/build/main.<sp/>This<sp/>will<sp/>open<sp/>HTTP<sp/>(port<sp/>8080)<sp/>and<sp/>MQTT<sp/>(port<sp/>1883,<sp/>topic<sp/>&quot;LED&quot;)<sp/>input<sp/>buffers.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">You<sp/>can<sp/>modify<sp/>`mqtt_publisher.cpp`<sp/>to<sp/>publish<sp/>different<sp/>JSONs<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>client,<sp/>or<sp/>use<sp/>any<sp/>other<sp/>MQTT<sp/>Client<sp/>to<sp/>publish<sp/>messages<sp/>to<sp/>topic<sp/>&quot;LED&quot;.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">You<sp/>can<sp/>send<sp/>JSONs<sp/>through<sp/>CURL<sp/>that<sp/>match<sp/>the<sp/>regex<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>documentation<sp/>to<sp/>change<sp/>LED<sp/>state.</highlight></codeline>
